<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/781646-why-are-humans-so-pretentious-to-assume">Why are humans so pretentious to assume that other animals don&#39;t think, don&#39;t feel, don&#39;t have consciousness, don&#39;t evolve, don&#39;t value life as we do?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_781646'><a id="like_count_community_question_781646" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/781646?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">37 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F22609485-the-soul-of-an-octopus">like</a></span>

