          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Audio CD 9781622316168" href="/book/show/22825702-the-soul-of-an-octopus">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/10361042-jailyn?shelf=memoir">memoir</a>, 
